{"tid":2262544,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（二次創作）其實youtube講解動漫班人點解可以盈利？","createTime":"2020-10-29T07:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:01:56.000Z","uid":69874,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5585a644a817b1556226df307b12f08bb2f37545","tid":2262544,"uid":69874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"利申先 唔係反佢地 純粹想討論下youtube係點樣判斷 因為聽聞有啲頻道都會有片下架<br />\n<br />\n例子就係台灣井村一，妮柯基慢<br />\n當然大陸佬佔左仲多 四季萌芽呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裡面內容基本上都係係啲動畫cut出黎 有啲會加埋動漫bgm 好奇點解有啲影片就會被下架 但又大部分都keep到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如四季萌芽一開頭啲片都唔見晒 <br />\n<br />\n少少off topic ，唔只動漫 講波講拳講電影果啲都係同一道理 其實youtube係咪已經默許左呢種二次創作去盈利？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己覺得有啲channel係有心做 幾岩拎黎重溫 有無巴打有研究過？"},{"pid":"bc0dacbcc16da2df1113ba82cac3d26ced412d2a","tid":2262544,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇點解有啲影片就會被下架 但又大部分都keep到</blockquote><br />\n因為KEEP到嗰啲你先睇到，被人DEL咗嗰啲你唔會知有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be7c09ef4206d2ccf15b65e0a5c536b7a59af15","tid":2262544,"uid":69874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc0dacbcc16da2df1113ba82cac3d26ced412d2a","tid":2262544,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇點解有啲影片就會被下架 但又大部分都keep到</blockquote><br />\n因為KEEP到嗰啲你先睇到，被人DEL咗嗰啲你唔會知有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁keep到果班又點解會keep到<br />\n<br />\n陰謀論ff 大陸狗keep到好似特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76aebaa7660476efdca5881da42a047eafdcdf9","tid":2262544,"uid":58998,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"