差唔多<br />\n<br />\n但好多都無創意就真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"果view數根本同電影受歡迎程度有關<br />\n同評論高質與否無關"},{"pid":"cf244611bb014512a995dabeb51574070a385059","tid":2262544,"uid":69874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a58936498dccc84671b6444d99d4b0f15671afe1","tid":2262544,"uid":236359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac0882603a59f7debbf55a7a1ebbcf098cb32c35","tid":2262544,"uid":69874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdfdb78efa4f54e83c0eecf66b4cea114cec259a","tid":2262544,"uid":356010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"其實根本係打撃緊真正有創意嘅人，同影響第一創作者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得未必既 例如巨人/獵人漫 多字多伏筆 啲人又似樣 睇得辛苦可以睇下呢啲解讀 同啲分析文差唔多<br />\n<br />\n但好多都無創意就真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"果view數根本同電影受歡迎程度有關<br />\n同評論高質與否無關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"係 所以好多都做受歡迎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但硬係有種魔力 睇過套野都入去睇晒條片"},{"pid":"d3bb0f25272bb24dc161b5bb18390bc951c4e8e9","tid":2262544,"uid":256957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b201313fb8e287a0ac9a4a64bb6acd811e65f605","tid":2262544,"uid":69874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"咁amv呢樣野大家又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲整到好熱血 但多數都係音樂有版權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"睇下咩類型 如果係靜止畫mad無咩問題 好支持<br />\n靜止畫mad要拎素材點都要做少少preprocess先至可以去做editing<br />\n而當中editing又可以有3d scene and transition, tune色, sfx, character animation, motion graphic<br />\n基本上靜止畫mad利用部份作品素材 + 大部份自己心機去完成一個video content<br />\n要用大量editing去突顯作品/敘述故事<br />\n整得好睇有至少一半都係歸於自editing<br />\naudio/image source只係其次 所以覺得無咩問題<br />\n<br />\n如果只係求其cut啲動畫clip加少少opacity transition嘅個類動畫mad就好撚有問題<br />\n用晒人地動畫畫面調幾下位置crop精華就等同創作真係好戇鳩<br />\n大部份amv感覺就係班細蚊仔啱啱學完windows movie maker加youtube-dl整出嚟ge作品<br />\n如果加埋少少中二病19標題仲吃香<br />\n好似咩<br />\n<blockquote>love is beautiful pain<br />\nSayonara I Love You<br />\n只要有你就好了，希望你能一直在身旁微笑</blockquote><br />\n仲有個啲複合mad 九唔撚搭八clip埋一齊<br />\n連想表達啲咩都已經睇唔透 畫面靚極都係靠本身條clip 唔洗effort<br />\nclip一clip神作畫scene就已經done一套amv<br />\n十套有7~8套都係咁撚樣<br />\n啲賣點完全唔會係editing 係睇clip靚唔靚 歌好唔好聽<br />\nclip fade in/out個陣同首歌節奏夾唔夾就算 完全無effort可言<br />\n當effort低成咁我覺得已經侵緊權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8e58e918f0f04dc89ba3a27a706795dd692a5c","tid":2262544,"uid":25100,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9d5f4fc2b84e2f4682e2012107b4ee37025ea98","tid":2262544,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"92bb90bba518d415595af2b7ddc99dc7e3cb36ef","tid":2262544,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3453f4cbea080063a57af4b012409010df3798","tid":2262544,"uid":236359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"重複講翻果套電影的內容果d垃圾 <br />\n都有幾十萬view 我真係笑撚咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"睇下咩類型<br />\n谷阿莫垃圾, honest trailer咪正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"谷阿莫邊到唔得，速睇一部電影喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:03:06.000Z","msg":"你返去食屎啦"},{"pid":"35a71bb61b599325959cf718fb1dc65de569e87f","tid":2262544,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d5f4fc2b84e2f4682e2012107b4ee37025ea98","tid":2262544,"uid":360800,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"92bb90bba518d415595af2b7ddc99dc7e3cb36ef","tid":2262544,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3453f4cbea080063a57af4b012409010df3798","tid":2262544,"uid":236359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"重複講翻果套電影的內容果d垃圾 <br />\n都有幾十萬view 我真係笑撚咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"睇下咩類型<br />\n谷阿莫垃圾, honest trailer咪正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"谷阿莫邊到唔得，速睇一部電影喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi